BootStrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%labels
Author DeploymentPrep
Description Container with initial log state for deployment-report task.

%post
    set -e

    ############################
    # 1. Install requirements  #
    ############################
    apt-get update
    DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        python3-pip \
        ca-certificates \
        && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    ############################
    # 2. Create directory tree #
    ############################
    LOG_DIR="/home/user/deployment/logs"
    mkdir -p "${LOG_DIR}"

    ############################
    # 3. Populate log files    #
    ############################
    cat > "${LOG_DIR}/2023-09-01.log" <<'EOF'
2023-09-01 02:15:12 [web-01] STATUS: OK
2023-09-01 02:16:05 [db-01] STATUS: FAIL
2023-09-01 02:17:45 [cache-01] STATUS: OK
2023-09-01 02:18:20 [auth-01] STATUS: FAIL
EOF

    cat > "${LOG_DIR}/2023-09-02.log" <<'EOF'
2023-09-02 02:14:02 [web-02] STATUS: OK
2023-09-02 02:15:47 [db-02] STATUS: OK
2023-09-02 02:16:37 [cache-02] STATUS: OK
2023-09-02 02:18:55 [auth-02] STATUS: OK
EOF

    cat > "${LOG_DIR}/2023-09-03.log" <<'EOF'
2023-09-03 02:13:33 [web-03] STATUS: OK
2023-09-03 02:15:02 [db-03] STATUS: FAIL
2023-09-03 02:16:58 [cache-03] STATUS: FAIL
2023-09-03 02:17:42 [auth-03] STATUS: OK
EOF

    ############################
    # 4. Set permissions       #
    ############################
    # Ensure users of any UID can create /home/user/deployment/reports later
    chmod 0777 /home/user /home/user/deployment

    # Logs should be readable but not necessarily writable
    chmod 0755 "${LOG_DIR}"
    chmod 0644 "${LOG_DIR}"/*.log

%environment
    chmod 755 /home/user

    # Nothing to override; rely on default HOME binding.

%runscript
    echo "Container for deployment-report task.  Use this as your execution environment."

%help
This Apptainer image provides the exact initial filesystem state required for
the deployment-report exercise.  It contains:

  • Python 3 and pytest (available system-wide).
  • The directory /home/user/deployment/logs/ with the three raw log files.

No report directories or files have been created.